Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/place/Geometry
Object: A geographic extent expressed as a point, box or polygon.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/place/hasPlaceType
Object: Relates a place to a place type.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/place/PlaceType
Object: A place type e.g. town, constituency, county, country.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/place/hasGeometry
Object: Relates a place to its geometric representation.

Subject: http://parliament.uk/ontologies/place/containedByPlace
Object: Relates a place to a place it is contained by e.g. town in constituency in county in country.
